Author: Julia Serrago
Content:
-Kathleen Loso pure celery juice on an empty stomach every morning - wait 15-30 minutes before having anything else. 
Drink pure cucumber juice, pure coconut water, lemon water, lime water these are hydrating. Vimergy micro C - it contains some silica and helps. Eat, blend and juice lots of leafy greens and herbs such as parsley and arugula. More fruit and berries Artichoke, Asparagus, Kale stems. This brand silica too - Orgono Living Silica Siliplant. Lower fats in your diet. (Skin is Liver related)
Look up “Medical Medium Skin Potion”. He also has a podcast episode “Skin, Hair, & Nail Health”
